---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Clinician Consultations | Morning Tide Consulting and Collective"
	description="Clinician consultation for mental health billing, insurance workflows, credentialing, and practice operations."
>
	<main class="px-6 py-16 lg:px-10 lg:py-20">
		<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-8">
			<p class="eyebrow">Clinician Consultations</p>
			<h1 class="max-w-4xl text-5xl leading-none text-(--color-ink) sm:text-6xl">Consulting for clinicians navigating billing, insurance, and practice operations.</h1>
			<p class="max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-(--color-muted)">
				For clinicians who want experienced guidance around mental health billing, insurance systems, credentialing, and the operational side of running a practice.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mx-auto mt-12 grid max-w-6xl gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr]">
			<div class="section-shell rounded-[2rem] p-8">
				<p class="eyebrow">What this covers</p>
				<h2 class="mt-4 text-4xl leading-none text-(--color-ink)">Practical support with operational depth.</h2>
				<ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-(--color-muted)">
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-(--color-brand)"></span><span>Insurance billing workflows and documentation habits</span></li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-(--color-brand)"></span><span>Credentialing and paneling strategy</span></li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-(--color-brand)"></span><span>Systems refinement for private practice operations</span></li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-(--color-brand)"></span><span>Consultation tailored to the clinician’s current stage and bottlenecks</span></li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div id="book-a-call" class="rounded-[2rem] border border-(--color-line-soft) bg-(--color-surface) p-8 shadow-(--shadow-soft)">
				<p class="eyebrow">Book a Consultation</p>
				<h2 class="mt-4 text-4xl leading-none text-(--color-ink)">Clear next steps for clinicians who want direct expertise.</h2>
				<p class="mt-5 text-base leading-8 text-(--color-muted)">
					Add your booking link, availability, and consultation format here.
				</p>
				<a class="mt-8 inline-flex rounded-full bg-(--color-accent) px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-(--shadow-brand)" href="/#contact">
					Request a clinician consultation
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="faq" class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-6xl rounded-[2rem] border border-(--color-line-soft) bg-(--color-surface) p-8 shadow-(--shadow-soft)">
			<p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
			<h2 class="mt-4 text-4xl leading-none text-(--color-ink)">Questions clinicians often ask before booking.</h2>
			<div class="mt-6 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3">
				<div>
					<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-(--color-ink)">Who is this best for?</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-(--color-muted)">Clinicians who want experienced support with the insurance and operational side of practice.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-(--color-ink)">What can a consultation include?</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-(--color-muted)">Workflow review, billing questions, credentialing guidance, and strategy around practice systems.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-(--color-ink)">How should this be booked?</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-(--color-muted)">Use this area for session length, format, and scheduling details once your booking workflow is ready.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
